2 & 4\end{array}\right]^{T}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{a}_{2}=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
3 & 5\end{array}\right]^{T}$
\end_inset

 that comes out zero.
