\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\begin{array}{cc|c}
2 & 3 & 0\\
4 & 5 & 0
\end{array}\right]\underrightarrow{R_{2}\gets R_{2}-2R_{1}}\left[\begin{array}{cc|c}
2 & 3 & 0\\
0 & -1 & 0
\end{array}\right].
\]

\end_inset

The bottom row encodes the equation 
\begin_inset Formula $-x_{2}=0$
\end_inset

.
