 important to understand what happens for systems of any size.
 If after row reduction of an 
\begin_inset Formula $m\times m$
\end_inset

 matrix we find 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

 zero rows, then there will be 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

