\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sin\theta_{ba}=\frac{a_{x}}{\left\Vert \mathbf{a}\right\Vert }\frac{b_{y}}{\left\Vert \mathbf{b}\right\Vert }-\frac{a_{y}}{\left\Vert \mathbf{a}\right\Vert }\frac{b_{x}}{\left\Vert \mathbf{b}\right\Vert }.
\]

\end_inset

Then compute the area using equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
