reference "eq:ParallelogramArea"

\end_inset

 and the expansion of 
\begin_inset Formula $\sin\theta_{ba}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{Area}\left(P\right)=\left\Vert \mathbf{a}\right\Vert \left\Vert \mathbf{b}\right\Vert \sin\theta_{ba}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
=a_{x}b_{y}-a_{y}b_{x}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
=\det\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a_{x} & b_{x}\\
a_{y} & b_{y}
